The Member class represents a member of the gym and is comparable based on name. Each Member object contains member information including first name, last name, date of birth, membership expiration date, and location. A member is uniquely identified by first name, last name, and date of birth. This class also offers other methods of comparison including by expiration date and by county/zipcode.
